%F A084081 a(2*n+1) = (3*n-1)*binomial(3*n+1, n)/((n+1)*(3*n+1)).
%F A084081 a(2*n) = 10*binomial(3*n+1, n-1)/(2*n+3). (End)
%F A084081 a(n) ~ c * 3^(3*(n+1)/2) / (2^(n+3/2) * n^(3/2) * sqrt(Pi)), where c = 5 if n is even, and c = 3*sqrt(3) if n is odd. - _Amiram Eldar_, Jan 09 2026
